The paper introduces a new method for improving neural networks' capacity to handle complex data with hierarchical and power-law structure. This is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
